CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Smithfield is an American food company and an industry leader in value-added packaged meats and fresh pork. We maintain high-quality standards, meeting demand through our strong relationships with thousands of U.S. family farmers and blue-chip global customers. We market our products under a leading portfolio of iconic brands including Smithfield, Eckrich and Nathan's Famous, among many others.
